I care deeply about everyone. I’ll be reaching out personally to certain ppl and sponsors…  I am here with my story and hopes to impact our youth and have them learn from my successes and failures. Swimming means the world to me and has done so many things for my life and the people around me. I hope to continue to grow the sport. I am pumped to watch everyone compete who work so hard to represent their countries it is such a memorable experience. I will be watching and cheering you all on! Thanks again for all the love and support. Go kick some ass!! #teamusa
